{"tid":1698160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔/admin入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-07T10:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T10:18:54.000Z","uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03e629b7ac54f12a8761f529f7ade7b4c49db9c7","tid":1698160,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知你好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要hold住個server<br />\n又要驚畀人ddos<br />\n不過希望你參考下呢度嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 新增減去熱門分數的方法</span><br />\n我唔知道「拉」係唔係真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為唔係官方說明有呢個功能<br />\n如果冇用<br />\n我希望你新增呢個功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（因為據我所知，你瀏覽個post，都會對熱門分數有增加）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 新增對會員<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/<br />\n賜酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>功能</span><br />\n如果我冇記錯<br />\n舊燈嗰個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">派膠/賜酒</span><br />\n係會影響到<span style=\"color: red;\">上熱門嘅機會</span><br />\n膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅數量越多 : 越難上熱門<br />\n酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅數量越多 : 較容易上熱門/對上熱門分數有加成<br />\netc.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 雙重驗證功能</span><br />\n呢樣冇乜可以講<br />\n連仔應該整緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要一樣 : FORCE LOGOUT</span><br />\n我唔知連仔仲有冇關注草泥馬（高登）嘅動向<br />\n事實上佢喺八月頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曾經過force logout 過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n而佢force logout 嘅方法係 : <br />\n<br />\n<em>首先下一至兩個星期之前出post通知會員<br />\n要求會員自己改密碼<br />\n去到一個限期前<br />\n佢都唔願意改密碼<br />\n先至強制force logout 呢一班人<br />\n而如果成功改密碼<br />\nSend一封電郵去佢嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">備用電郵<br />\n ( a.k.a.唔係isp嗰一個 ) </span><br />\n通知佢改咗新密碼<br />\n同時要求撳入個網址度<br />\n確認佢改咗新密碼</em><br />\n如此一來<br />\n就可以force logout 殭屍account/ 被盜用帳戶<br />\n又唔會對server造成太大負荷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道有啲point係比較難實行<br />\n但係我希望連仔可以盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗連仔都唔希望連登畀五毛入侵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認同請幫推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同一個post<br />\n我喺站務檯開過一次<br />\n如果方便<br />\n幫手推埋呢一個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n連仔/Admin 入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698157</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48ffec30e3679877a4cb70f8967a6b74116a2233","tid":1698160,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ad7b30bda401a68258ef862872ee74a0291940","tid":1698160,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"係唔係冇人睇我啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd17d01b83cdc656a40ecd1ce8ae2d29441e6d7c","tid":1698160,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:08:04.000Z"